<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pariksha | Secure Assessment Platform</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --midnight-blue: #1E3A8A;
      --midnight-blue-dark: #172f75;
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --line: #dbe3f1;
      --panel: #ffffff;
      --soft-bg: #f6f8fc;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", "Roboto", "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .top-nav {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: var(--midnight-blue);
      color: #fff;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ink);
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .nav-link-soft {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav-link-soft:hover {
      color: var(--midnight-blue);
    }

    .btn-nav-login {
      background: var(--midnight-blue);
      border: 1px solid var(--midnight-blue);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-nav-login:hover {
      background: var(--midnight-blue-dark);
      border-color: var(--midnight-blue-dark);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--midnight-blue) 0%, #1a367f 60%, var(--midnight-blue-dark) 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 4.2rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d6def0;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 2.8vw, 2.65rem);
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      color: #e2e8f0;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }

    .trust-note {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: #dbeafe;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .role-note {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #c7d2fe;
    }

    .btn-student {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--midnight-blue);
      border: 1px solid #fff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.68rem 1.1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-student:hover {
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: var(--midnight-blue-dark);
    }

    .mock-browser {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #d4ddef;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.2);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .mock-browser-top {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .dot.red { background: #ef4444; }
    .dot.yellow { background: #f59e0b; }
    .dot.green { background: #22c55e; }

    .address-bar {
      margin-left: 0.35rem;
      background: #eef2ff;
      border: 1px solid #dbe3f1;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 0.18rem 0.55rem;
    }

    .mock-content {
      padding: 1rem;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .mock-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .mock-title {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .mock-sub {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .timer-pill {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #b91c1c;
      background: #fef2f2;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .question-box {
      border: 1px solid #dbe3f1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.72rem 0.82rem;
      background: #f8fbff;
      font-size: 0.87rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .option-row {
      border: 1px solid #dde4f1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.52rem 0.65rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      color: #1f2937;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .progress-wrap {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      padding-top: 0.65rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .progress-text {
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .section-info {
      background: var(--soft-bg);
      padding: 3.2rem 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      font-size: 1.55rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-head p {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 70ch;
    }

    .info-card {
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.05rem;
    }

    .info-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #eaf0ff;
      color: var(--midnight-blue);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .info-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.62;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #fff;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 1.15rem 0;
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: var(--midnight-blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      color: var(--midnight-blue-dark);
    }



    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 3rem 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="top-nav">
    <div class="container py-3 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap gap-3">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
        <span class="brand-mark"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill"></i></span>
        <span class="brand-title">Pariksha Assessment Platform</span>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
        <a href="/login" class="btn-nav-login">Login</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <h1 class="hero-title">Redefining Academic Integrity</h1>
            <p class="hero-sub">
              Pariksha is a secure and practical examination system for institutions that need trusted proctoring, accessible test experiences, and reliable academic reporting.
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
              <a href="/login" class="btn-student">Login to Pariksha</a>
            </div>
            <p class="role-note mb-0">Single sign-in for students, faculty, and admin. Access is assigned by role after login.</p>
            <p class="trust-note mb-0">Trusted by educators. Built for students and administrators.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="mock-browser">
              <div class="mock-browser-top">
                <span class="dot red"></span>
                <span class="dot yellow"></span>
                <span class="dot green"></span>
                <span class="address-bar">secure.pariksha.edu/exam/attempt</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mock-content">
                <div class="mock-header">
                  <div>
                    <div class="mock-title">Business Analytics Midterm</div>
                    <div class="mock-sub">Question 12 of 30</div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="timer-pill"><i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i> 00:27:41</span>
                </div>

                <div class="question-box">
                  Which type of chart is most appropriate for comparing changes in enrollment trends across five academic years?
                </div>

                <div class="option-row">A. Pie Chart</div>
                <div class="option-row">B. Scatter Plot</div>
                <div class="option-row">C. Line Graph</div>
                <div class="option-row">D. Heatmap</div>

                <div class="progress-wrap">
                  <div class="progress-text">Progress: 40% complete</div>
                  <div class="progress" role="progressbar" aria-label="Exam progress" aria-valuenow="40" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <div class="progress-bar bg-primary" style="width: 40%"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-info">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Built for Real Academic Workflows</h2>
          <p>A focused and dependable system designed for classroom assessments, remote invigilation, and institutional reporting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <article class="info-card">
              <span class="info-icon"><i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i></span>
              <h3>Security</h3>
              <p>Real-time tab monitoring and browser lockdown help maintain exam integrity while giving administrators a clear event trail.</p>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <article class="info-card">
              <span class="info-icon"><i class="bi bi-book"></i></span>
              <h3>Education</h3>
              <p>Student-focused flows include the Text-to-Speech Listen feature to support accessibility and improve exam clarity.</p>
            </article>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <article class="info-card">
              <span class="info-icon"><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line"></i></span>
              <h3>Analytics</h3>
              <p>Faculty and admin teams can drill down by class, exam, and outcomes to review pass/fail trends and performance insights.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span>Pariksha &copy; 2026. Institutional Assessment Infrastructure.</span>
      <a href="/login">Unified Login Portal</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
